race.comment: HOT HAILEY (6) was quickly into stride and burnt early from the middle draw where she gave a sight, finishing second (17.46) and beaten a neck over 300m at this track. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from four starts. Leading chance again. GIGGLING DIXIE (1) turned in a plain run last time when seventh at this track over 300m behind TRICKY TOODLES (18.06) in a Mix 2/3. Form from her last run is proving strong. Should be about the mark. BALLYNEALE BULL (2) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 2 lengths away in third (17.85) behind Tralee Richie at this track. Can measure up. KATIE'S QUICK (4) boasts a solid strike-rate over this trip.
